{"_id":"DFhpwIxDX7t7Bfc2","name":"Talia the Sleeper","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-talia-the-sleeper.png","items":[{"_id":"rYhRbW2iQ1wPiTTa","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, \nmy mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that \nafflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving \nme from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending \ninjustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is \nsomeone who won’t break my heart.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, my mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that afflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving me from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending injustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is someone who won’t break my heart.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O56Uc0WUsSUOnoi8","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all \nkinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I \ntravel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true \ncondition from the world.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all kinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I travel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true condition from the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uZakjT9eq0DQ9H48","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or \nunderstand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate \nit when there are too many people around. The buzz of their \nlives reminds me of what I can’t have.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or understand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate it when there are too many people around. The buzz of their lives reminds me of what I can’t have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4SYJF1EOcEaq23VW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, \nI am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile \nand locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the \nleast caress, which would remind me of being alive.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, I am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile and locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the least caress, which would remind me of being alive.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6YmYNdNpQH5ZrIWE","name":"The Cloak","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y our large nun’s cloak floats to defend you from \nthe world and contains many small items that you can manipulate. \nThanks to this Gift you are able to float and hover in the air, but \nalways at a speed equal to the pace of a human. Once per Scene, \nyou may:\n1. Hide an object inside your cloak, hiding it from everyone (even \nwhen searching through magic).\n2. Extract from your cloak an object that you need. It can be rare \nand peculiar, but not magic or unique.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DjG1TOTxy9sJWAl8","name":"In the Dream","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can freely \ncommunicate with a subject who is unconscious through a \ndream. Alternatively, you may choose to spend 1 Soma to “read” \nthe dreams of a conscious subject. The Storyteller will reveal all or \npart of the subject’s Agenda to you through the narration of one \nof their dreams. Particularly powerful subjects and Hunters may \nrequire a Position Check to be able to capture their dreams.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TVpgljs2sjfwXLn9","name":"Dark Ego - The Sleeping Will","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use your power to \nmanipulate the objects around you. Y ou can make small items float or \nthrow them like weapons. Y ou can affect your surroundings up to 30 feet \naway. Y ou can act up to 3 times in an Exchange, manipulating the world \naround you, but you cannot act more than once against the same target. \nOnce per Scene, you can focus all 3 actions on a single large object (like a \nhouse) and manipulate it to your liking.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Shed your cloak, revealing your helpless body or exposing yourself \nto others by manipulating the world around you.","owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BLQIqhCneQRoGbh6","name":"A large nun’s cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A large nun’s cloak","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"B7F2985IGVepf44b","name":"A long hood with a veil hiding my face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A long hood with a veil hiding my face","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JJ5i6zBLBq1MkWIC","name":"Objects and small things that float under my cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"Objects and small things that float under my cloak","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"C22o1w61TWK8sHEO","name":"A piece of ivy that has remained clinging to my left arm","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":{"description":"A piece of ivy that has remained clinging to my left arm","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aDnHZPlDQIT0a4AL","name":"The diary in which I wrote about my sad life before the curse","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"equipment","sequence":5}},"system":{"description":"The diary in which I wrote about my sad life before the curse","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7pBkMjDSWYQ41hCM","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.talia-the-sleeper","ownerKey":"cazador.talia-the-sleeper","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24","owner":"Talia the Sleeper","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"source.talia-the-sleeper"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-talia-the-sleeper","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"24"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Talia the Sleeper","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, \nmy mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that \nafflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving \nme from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending \ninjustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is \nsomeone who won’t break my heart."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"HNZe6qeZ9UiUjZdS","name":"The Gang of three Pigs","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-the-gang-of-three-pigs.png","items":[{"_id":"o1An5fhLPpp9FFJO","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We \nwere a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with \nus the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a \nsecret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even \nreturn from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We were a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with us the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a secret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even return from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ssd0tqtX3UnZIsUK","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority \nto overcome our human limitations. Our faces \nare always covered by a pig’s head mask, \nintimidating ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority to overcome our human limitations. Our faces are always covered by a pig’s head mask, intimidating ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pxkviZNYvCOt8rSQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, \nour body is able to regenerate. We do not fear \npain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an \nobsession for us, and is more important than \nanything else.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, our body is able to regenerate. We do not fear pain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an obsession for us, and is more important than anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nJM7GByFQUbkU2cR","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We \nare very protective of what we think is ours.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We are very protective of what we think is ours.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QLU0VyhtrNJnULE5","name":"Gang","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can act as three independent \ncharacters using all the same Descriptors, Gifts and \nSoma. Each gang member has 1 single Wound, for a \ntotal of 3. Each of you is skilled at something.\nThe eldest gains 1 Additional Success in actions \ninvolving repairing or tampering with the \nenvironment. \nThe middle brother gains 1 Additional Success in \nactions to construct or tamper with objects.\nThe youngest gains 1 Additional Success in actions \nnot related to any kind of obligation or duty towards \nthe gang or the current mission.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y89zehE9ZTpYFFdH","name":"Eating the Divine","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"By eating the flesh, \nyou can regenerate your bodies and even return \nfrom death. At the end of each Scene, each member \nrecovers their Wound as long as at least one of the \nBrothers is still alive to activate the power of this Gift. \nOnce per Scenario, one of you can spend 1 Soma to \nheal immediately from 1 Wound and come back to \nlife instantly.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QHlch76mxAEjTbI1","name":"Dark Ego - Our Home","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"When you arrive in a new location, you can take the \ntime to examine, alter, and repair it. Y ou may use one of the following options for each \npresent gang member.\n1. Escape route: Detail a Descriptor that represents an escape route that only you \nmay open.\n2. Trap: Detail a Descriptor that describes how your trap activates and hurts intruders. \nThose who enter the perimeter will trigger it, suffering 1 Wound. Skilled and attentive \nindividuals may require a Position Check to fall into your trap.\n3. Improvement: Create a Descriptor that represents an improvement you make to \nthe environment. Y ou get 1 Additional Success when you make use of your improvement \nduring an action.\n4. Alter: Detail a Descriptor that represents a new feature of the site that only you can \nactivate.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take time to work on a location and make it your own.","owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WKFQQX00BpuywbmD","name":"Pig’s head masks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Pig’s head masks","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.the-gang-of-three-pigs"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O470Fod0ix3cONL0","name":"Carpenter’s tool bags","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Gang of three Pigs","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.the-gang-of-three-pigs","ownerKey":"cazador.the-gang-of-three-pigs","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Carpenter’s tool bags","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].