><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SGqiDf5WLWMdMXhr","name":"Hatta Carter","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-hatta-carter.png","items":[{"_id":"lrSXmQoZcfrn1brH","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can \ncomplete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes \nI lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to \ncomplete the simplest actions.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can complete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes I lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to complete the simplest actions.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5kxos0NIGo60KqLb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can \nperform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch \nof my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they \nshould.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can perform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch of my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they should.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HNUOTT0ELCLEHtOe","name":"Time Watches","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"When you want to use time to your \nadvantage, you can twist the stem on one of your watches and choose \nfrom the following. \n1. Slow the World Down: Receive 1 Additional Success to your \nnext Position Check.\n2. Speed up the Hatter: Y ou can act immediately (unless you \nhave already done so during the Exchange) by interrupting anyone’s \naction, regardless of what else might be happening in the narrative. \nWhen you use your watches, you gain 1 Time Token. During the \nScenario, the Storyteller can spend 1 Time Token to freeze you a few \nseconds in time and give you 2 Penalties to a Defense Check. If you \ntake an Interlude and drink some good tea, you can discard all the \nTime Tokens you have accumulated.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"T6W8MVlS2t13rQkV","name":"Playmates","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou own three automated dolls, The Little \nHatter, The Hare, and The Dormouse. Each automaton can perform \nsmall tasks, such as picking up and carrying items or delivering a \nmessage. Each doll has a special ability.\nThe Little Hatter can explode, inflicting 1 Wound to everyone \nwithin ten feet of it. \nThe Hare can always find a way, even through narrow places or \nclosed doors. \nThe Dormouse can fall asleep and deactivate to discard 1 Time \nToken. \nDuring Interludes, repair all automata.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GHyoiegNEgKsiKJ8","name":"Dark Ego - Mad like a Hatter","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"When you give free rein to \nyour madness, reality bends itself to prove you right. Declare something \ncrazy such as That door leads to the opposite side of town, or This pair \nof glasses allows you to see ghosts and create a Descriptor. Y our madness \nmust always concern an object and its crazy use. Y ou cannot directly affect \nor interact with living beings. Suffer 1 Wound caused by the fatigue of \nturning your madness into reality. Y our madness lasts throughout the \nScene. If at least one subject is amazed by what you do with your madness, \nyou gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Behave and talk like a crazy person, not worrying about the \nreactions of those around you.","owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kMBhfwX91Ce06ihw","name":"A valuable and improbably tall top hat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A valuable and improbably tall top hat","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cmHWzGcNBH8osdgI","name":"Evening clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Evening clothes","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6TujfkMfO4NjdKBT","name":"Watchmaker’s shirts and glasses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.hatta-carter","ownerKey":"cazador.hatta-carter","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"Watchmaker’s shirts and glasses","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Hatta Carter","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.hatta-carter"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xWNad001pRz01isj","name":"A complete set of over twenty watches","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","