{"_id":"c56zCGegdLD5DMQc","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-iskra-the-young-wolf.png","items":[{"_id":"BvUyqVnB2F4xAH3e","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the \nHunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do \neverything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the Hunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do everything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bx5DP6QAHzxHMf4b","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child \nand, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to \nbehave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed \nforever.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child and, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to behave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed forever.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S9j04snAvCOKwCBL","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting \ncompanions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the \npack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important \nthan me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting companions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the pack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important than me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rx4HRwAS8UduuaIG","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Iskra the\n Young\nWolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My \nsense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the \nworld, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t \nknow.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Iskra the Young Wolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My sense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the world, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fzwj3zBsNNAjwcXx","name":"The Red Hood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma to look exactly like \na common child. Create a Descriptor that contains one of the words \nPretty, Small, or Sweet. As long as you maintain your disguise, no \nadult will notice you or consider you a potential danger. Receive 2 \nAdditional Successes to the first action you take when you decide to \ndrop your disguise and reveal who you are.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"y4ej5KaKhKoaJSH6","name":"Pack","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"When you coordinate and act with one or more of your \nteammates against a common threat, you both get 1 Additional Success \nfor your Position Check. At the end of the Scene, if you have resolved \na significant issue thanks to the collaboration with your companions, \nyou recover 1 Soma.\nIwas abandoned by my mother in a large forest and survived by joining a pack of werewolves. After \na year of honing my predatory skills, I tracked down the woman I once called “Mother” and sank \nmy fangs into her throat. My pack was dismantled by a group of Hunters and the Order captured me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RG1dV8MWpe0nIdAA","name":"Dark Ego - The Young Wolf","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Unleash your feral side, ready to bite anyone who opposes your pack. If you get an Outcome with an \nIncrement on a Position Check, you can spend the Increment to take an \nadditional action immediately. Y ou can also inflict 1 Wound on yourself \nto perform an additional action after your normal action. Y ou can’t \nperform more than 3 actions per Exchange. Y ou may spend 1 Soma \nto memorize the smell of a person you are interacting with. Y ou will \nalways recognize them and it will be easy for you to follow their tracks \neven after a long time.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Give free rein to your feral side or fulfill a task for your pack with your wolf skills.\nXP\nSoma\n 6","owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kcIX8jdPsmvBQeBR","name":"A red cape of fine workmanship, embroidered with the coat of arms of the Order","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A red cape of fine workmanship, embroidered with the coat of arms of the Order","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"W46CUmfkaLlqgPCU","name":"A wolf mask carved in wood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A wolf mask carved in wood","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CFiXI2IEX2d79tHW","name":"A broken clay doll, a memento of one of my few happy memories of my mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"A broken clay doll, a memento of one of my few happy memories of my mother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0kaBORhnRXDFJZ1r","name":"A fang from the leader of my old pack","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":{"description":"A fang from the leader of my old pack","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L6rrs33PpZeBpmbA","name":"A rag doll depicting a well-dressed girl, a gift from my beloved grandmother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":5}},"system":{"description":"A rag doll depicting a well-dressed girl, a gift from my beloved grandmother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5rkFIGNay23CMcd4","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.iskra-the-young-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.iskra-the-young-wolf","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14","owner":"Iskra the Young Wolf","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"source.iskra-the-young-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-iskra-the-young-wolf","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"14"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Iskra the Young Wolf","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the \nHunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do \neverything the alpha Hunter asks of me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fgUPyDrK8LZWQetx","name":"Bloodwhite","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-bloodwhite.png","items":[{"_id":"PoeTxaYNQa6FRcql","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses \nmy unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, \nmy body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close \nto me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses my unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, my body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NqZd9pRsnOFMyPY8","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating \nresults. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the \ngrip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am \nafraid to touch the people I care about.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating results. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the grip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am afraid to touch the people I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YpeEaNL3h6tg6b23","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My \npure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to \navoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a \nmonster.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My pure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to avoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a monster.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"398ofO7eaA9Wvvc1","name":"Mutant","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 3 Mutation Tokens. \nY ou may spend 1 Mutation Token to modify a part of your body, \nsuch as turning your arms into wings or your skin into a thick \ncarapace. Create a Descriptor that represents the mutation. Y ou \ngain 1 Additional Success whenever you take advantage of your \nmutation. Whenever you change shape, the Storyteller can decide \nthat the hormone emitted by your body bewilders the mind of an \nNPC nearby, creating a specific Agenda for them that leads them \nto seek you in some way. Y our mutations remain until the end of \nthe Scene. Once per Scenario, the Storyteller can declare that this \nGift is activated without you realizing it and give you 1 Mutation \nToken.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NSHpPh5KwwMeHLdq","name":"Mutagenic Touch","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can inflict 1 Wound to a living \nbeing with the touch of your hand. If you kill the target this way, \nit will explode in a gruesome way, scaring everyone present. The \nmost impressionable NPCs, at the Storyteller’s discretion, will \nthen try to avoid any confrontation with you. When you achieve \nan Outcome with an Increment with your touch and kill someone, \nyour body assimilates part of the exploded flesh, and you may \nrecover 1 Mutation Token or 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AyLNCkYHvzX6wrzE","name":"Dark Ego - Pure Innocence","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"When you appeal to the \npurity of your heart, even the foulest spell is broken. When you \nactivate your Dark Ego during a Scene, you become immune to \nany effect of fear or mind control, and all subjects you consider evil \nlower their Opposition Level by 1 in your presence. Y ou can spend 1 \nMutation Token to give 1 Additional Success to the first action of all \nallies who admire you for who you are.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Open your heart and appeal to the goodness of those close to \nyou, revealing who you are, or sacrifice something of yourself for others.\nXP\nSoma\n 5","owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZhAqApLDk3FrTFwb","name":"A precious dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A precious dress","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"axbkH1OWvuzdftQ9","name":"A swallow-shaped hair clip, a gift from my mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A swallow-shaped hair clip, a gift from my mother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jnOooTsU2Nf5iv8I","name":"An old gun, a gift from a group of seven mercenaries who defended me for a long time","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"An old gun, a gift from a group of seven mercenaries who defended me for a long time","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"q3uLcDdq5UjuYvNz","name":"The coat of arms of my noble family","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":{"description":"The coat of arms of my noble family","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gQa5Uuxa4HX24GAf","name":"A few small animals from the woods that follow me, attracted by my smell","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"equipment","sequence":5}},"system":{"description":"A few small animals from the woods that follow me, attracted by my smell","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DMjeMZZSnzBcfQ0I","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.bloodwhite","ownerKey":"cazador.bloodwhite","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6","owner":"Bloodwhite","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"source.bloodwhite"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-bloodwhite","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Bloodwhite","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fh0x6pzWUMXLhzpA","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales.png","items":[{"_id":"RULHqvOhbFhj5iI1","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories \nand poems.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories and poems.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jWpXp8NGezoBu68n","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw \na lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to \nlearn a new story.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw a lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to learn a new story.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SOEMkcSdGlNUNq2I","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best \ncompliment others to make them feel good. I will not \ntolerate those who use violence.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best compliment others to make them feel good. I will not tolerate those who use violence.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0AfYVXeAyOVcTzuH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Sherazade \nthe Weaver of \nTales\nMy stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of \nreality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom \nhas made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales My stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of reality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom has made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"k2fPQ4t08c1JCzeq","name":"The Tale","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start each Scenario with 3 Story Tokens. \nOnce per Scene, you may tell a short story. If you do, spend \n1 Story Token and declare a Keyword that appears in your \nnarrative, then mark it down on your Sheet. During the \nScenario, if a Keyword you have marked is introduced during \na Scene by the Storyteller (for example, the Keyword is Soldier \nand you come across Soldiers), erase the word to get 1 XP and \n2 Additional Successes for either your next action or that of \none of your allies. When you learn an interesting new story, \nyou receive 1 Story Token.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EDSpX6a4QW9K4amc","name":"Words Like Honey","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can speak beautiful words \nto bring out a memory, an emotion, or a fear. Spend 1 Story \nToken and choose one Keyword. Each NPC or Hunter who \nhas listened to you and is connected to the Keyword will \nbe overwhelmed by their emotions and will have to create \na relevant Descriptor and keep it throughout the Scene. \nParticularly powerful subjects and Hunters who oppose your \npower may require a Position Check. Y our allies receive 1 \nAdditional Success in the first action they take when using \nany Descriptor created by this Gift.\nI am the greatest storyteller that has ever lived, having learned my skills after serving a \nwealthy sultan for many years. I can’t remember why I left, but I suddenly found myself in \nEurope, where I used my skills against the Order and the Hunters. After my defeat, I was \nforgiven, for it was clear to my jailers that a dark force had clouded my mind. I serve the Order \nto regain my freedom, but also to find the one who corrupted my heart, forcing me to do harm.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"l5JS02yIBQ9u1mhp","name":"Dark Ego - One Thousand and One Nights","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"One of the \ncharacters in a story you told during the Session comes to life as a Shadow. \nCreate a Descriptor for them, ensuring it is driven to support you. The \nShadow could, for example, fly or walk on water. The Shadow thus created \nwill be at your service and will do whatever you order with an OL Medium 5 \nand 1 Wound. For each Story Token you decide to spend, you can summon \nan additional Shadow. Y our Shadows do not speak and cannot act in places \nwhere there is more light than darkness.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Manifest your affinity for the shadows or tell a dark story full of \nfear and monsters.\nXP\nSoma\n 6","owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"mF20wV3IR6wEw7D5","name":"Precious oriental dresses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Precious oriental dresses","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3BNWEzG3SDsZzbnY","name":"A veil of red silk with which to cover my face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","ownerKey":"cazador.sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A veil of red silk with which to cover my face","n