ifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"mzuef3Aka7F7Ivdq","name":"Morgana of the Lake","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-morgana-of-the-lake.png","items":[{"_id":"cj9FFtsApB7qTiKw","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. \nDreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving \nme a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things \nI’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will \nhappen in the future of someone I care about.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. Dreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving me a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things I’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will happen in the future of someone I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"601XIffXSf74V1Bq","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure \ntricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors \nand sleights of hand.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure tricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors and sleights of hand.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"x1O1AMb8kGJS0z5S","name":"Weaver of Destiny","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can give a goal \nto an ally, such as Defeat that enemy or Retrieve that item. As \nlong as your ally acts to fulfill the destiny you have indicated to \nthem, they get 1 Additional Success to all their actions. However, \nif at the end of the Scene you have not achieved your goal, you will \nboth suffer 1 Wound due to the magical backlash of destiny. When \nfaced with one or more choices, you can spend 1 Soma and ask the \nUniverse to help you decide. Choose a Keyword such as enemy, \ndanger, or something else and the Storyteller will tell you which \nof the possibilities in front of you is the most related to the word \nyou have chosen.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9mSJWBFqT2SqxSPS","name":"Illusion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou may spend 1 Soma to create up to three \nillusions and move them as you like. Create a Descriptor that \nrepresents your illusions. Every illusion is a distortion of the \nvisual field. Y ou may make them more believable by adding 1 \nelement, choosing from between sound, smell, or tactility. Y our \nillusions are realistic, but they will be exposed if closely examined. \nAlternatively, you may spend 1 Soma to create three illusory \ncopies of yourself to confuse watchers. Y ou gain 3 Additional \nSuccesses for the first Defense Check you make. Y ou then subtract \n1 Additional Success (down to zero) for each additional Defense \nCheck you must take.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yvux6kf9GqLndmO0","name":"Dark Ego - The Supreme Fairy","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can unleash your true \nfairy essence and alter reality itself. When you do this, you suffer 1 Wound \nand choose an effect:\n1. Making the Unreal a Reality: One of your illusions becomes \nreal. If necessary, the Storyteller must create an ad hoc profile.\n2. Supreme Fairy: Y ou may replicate a Gift with a magical effect you \nhave witnessed at least once during the Scenario, for the duration of the \nScene.\n3. Lady of Destiny: Y ou can change the fate of a Minor NPC by \nrewriting its Descriptor and Agenda. This may not affect particularly \npowerful NPCs or enemies, at the Storyteller’s discretion.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Evoke your true potential when experiencing a strong emotion or \nwhen you find yourself in a magically charged location, and let yourself be \nflooded with power.","owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kuxwCyB8M9Q3cgLv","name":"A practical, street artist’s dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A practical, street artist’s dress","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9NA7GRtKoq2DPfyc","name":"A silver headband, a gift from someone I have forgotten","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A silver headband, a gift from someone I have forgotten","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.morgana-of-the-lake"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9YAEz9SuFdaZQGTo","name":"A small diary where I transcribe my dreams","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Morgana of the Lake","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.morgana-of-the-lake","ownerKey":"cazador.morgana-of-the-lake","role":"equipment","seq