{"_id":"rl4ro5zNZF0k3nlp","name":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet.png","items":[{"_id":"Xlwfzma0JXxGpKVX","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason \nI am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and \nmagic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and \nI move only because I pretend to be a real child.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason I am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and magic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and I move only because I pretend to be a real child.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vA8ilNOw8Cyv0KDk","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive \nto perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to \ntrust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive to perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to trust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fFp8xXwZ41UGIB6X","name":"Lies","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"When you tell a lie, you can temporarily make it a \nreality. Create a Descriptor that represents your lie and concerns \nsomething about you that you pride yourself on, such as: I have the \nstrength of five men, or I can fly through the air. The Descriptor \nremains throughout the Scene, and you gain 1 Additional Success \nthe first time you use it for an action. Each time you make use of this \nGift you receive 1 Lie Token. Y our nose will grow in proportion \nto the amount of Lie Tokens you have. During the Scenario the \nStoryteller can spend 1 Lie Token to give you 1 Penalty on a Check, \ndescribing how your clumsy puppet body prevents you from \nperforming at your best. With every Lie Token spent, your nose \nshrinks closer back to normal.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"07DD9ZbyFdsQzyFd","name":"Always in the Middle of Trouble","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, \nwhen you face a danger or problem arising from a previous choice \nyou have made, you recover 1 Soma and get 2 XP . When you do \nwhat an NPC asks and trust them without asking questions, you \ncan discard 1 Lie Token.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"e4wXNDY1iNUxPTRc","name":"Dark Ego - Soulless Puppet","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y our body is made of wood and \nso you ignore any penalty derived from dangers that would affect a living \nbeing. Y ou receive 1 Additional Success to all your Defense Checks. Y ou \ncan communicate with other puppets or toys who can tell you something \nat the Storyteller’s discretion. If you stay still, you will pass as a common \npuppet in the eyes of those who see you and you cannot be discovered \nexcept with special skills or magic.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Make obvious use of the wooden properties of your body to perform \nan action, or have your nose grow dramatically (i.e. when you accumulate \nthe third Lie Token), proving to everyone that you are not human.","owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X7BRUA3Wc737S8Dt","name":"A school coat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A school coat","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1UkFbR8SDv0EkyHa","name":"An old textbook","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"An old textbook","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Is5fjNYOMiZgjzEj","name":"A map to the famous Field of Miracles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","ownerKey":"cazador.wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"A map to the famous Field of Miracles","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.wound-car