{"_id":"zspv6Bhv7clRxoSQ","name":"OZena the Suffering","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-ozena-the-suffering.png","items":[{"_id":"THJzid1YB2umLkmE","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order \nis deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order is deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pFJ6N6d05YliUlTW","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking \nadvantage of the magical shoes I took from my first \nvictim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I \nam ashamed of my condition.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking advantage of the magical shoes I took from my first victim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I am ashamed of my condition.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ksd1It3n5hLlNdYt","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I \nknow how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my \nwill on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being \na stranger far from my home in time and space makes it \ndifficult to trust others.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I know how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my will on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being a stranger far from my home in time and space makes it difficult to trust others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OdqCfqM6aiUsmDtG","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and \nmagic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches \nand sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and magic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches and sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bUfWhfKdllpgVzzl","name":"The Silver Shoes","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"When you move, you can teleport \nfor short distances, and this allows you to automatically elude \nany attempt to impede or prevent your movements. Y ou need to \nsee where you intend to reappear. If you’re holding someone’s \nhand, you can spend 1 Soma to bring them with you. Once \nduring the Scenario, you may make a longer trip, even of \nseveral miles, but only to a place that you have seen at least once \nbefore.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don1.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9R6E7UYwYKjrFHPQ","name":"Experience of a Dark Journey","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou have \naccomplished many missions with strange companions and \nhave learned something from each of them. Y ou can invoke \neach of these effects once per Scenario.\n1. Tough as Tin: Ignore 1 Wound you should suffer from \nphysical damage. \n2. The Bravery of a Lion: Y ou gain 2 Additional Successes \nwhen you throw yourself against a great danger without caring \nabout the consequences.\n3. The Brain of a Genius Scarecrow: The Storyteller \nwill provide you with useful information about a place, \npersonality, or event you are dealing with. The information you \ngain is always useful to what you’re doing.\nI am a young American girl from 1939. Because of a magic tornado, I crashed into Broken Europe with a \nstrange doctor named Norman Henkle. I am suffering from a rare form of OZena, which disfigures my face \nand has blighted my life ever since I was a child. Dr. Henkle deceived me with the promise of a cure and a way \nback to my time, asking me to become a witch hunter. I committed crimes, even murders, until the Order put \nan end to my madness. I was forgiven and found in the Order a new home that I don’t want to run away from.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"don2.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"01DLuTuaTX54VIzj","name":"Dark Ego - From Another World","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"As a creature displaced in time, you \nare naturally resistant to magic. Y ou gain 2 Additional Successes when defending \nyourself from a danger associated with magic. When you inflict 1 Wound on a \nbeing associated with magic, you prevent them from using their powers (Gifts and \nDescriptors) during their next action. Blocking the powers of particularly powerful \nopponents and Hunters may require a Position Check. When you touch a magic or \nenchanted object, you can spend 1 Soma to temporarily interrupt its power. The \nduration of this effect is decided by the Storyteller.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Reveal that you’re from another time through a gesture or a word. \nAlternatively, act threatening towards a magical being.","owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"apG8qBvhhu6KZYLn","name":"A green cape with a wide and drooping hood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A green cape with a wide and drooping hood","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X9kng4KmZgcU8sdh","name":"A blade of modern design","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A blade of modern design","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"11hYl9G4miyKpu0N","name":"A bag full of small objects from my time","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"A bag full of small objects from my time","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.ozena-the-suffering"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RvlfnvR8bXusntWp","name":"A mask of delicate workmanship that depicts a suffering face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"OZena the Suffering","source":"The Broken Ones","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.ozena-the-suffering","ownerKey":"cazador.ozena-the-suffering","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":